cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.NI, cs.RO, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with traffic signal control using feedback and controllers, which are topics related to systems and control (cs.SY). The implementation of the controllers in a micro simulator involves artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and networked systems (cs.NI). The comparison of different controllers in different scenarios involves optimization and robotics (cs.RO). Finally, the use of simulations to evaluate the controllers involves machine learning (cs.LG).
